There are several key factors to be considered for the experimental test and development of this concept. Firstly, the gap between the two foils plays an important role, because it determines the electron energy, density and flux. Since the carbon ion front moves with the proton layer, we can estimate the foil transparency time τ implicitly as5G+2L>2c×∫0τβdt=2c∫0τ(1−[ν(t)+υ(t)]1/3−[ν(t)−υ(t)]1/3)dt.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
